These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, project-manager, librarian
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, subway, trike
1. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
2. the librarian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
3. the person driving the trike is between the project-manager and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | project-manager | social-worker   | librarian |
| Transport   | subway | trike | taxi        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, iced-tea
3 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, bird
1. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the horse##7
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk   | sprite   |
| Pet        | guinea-pig | bird | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, banana, pomegranate
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, motorbike
1. the person eating radish is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
2. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the person eating radish and the person driving the van##7
3. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | banana | pomegranate | radish |
| Transport   | van       | motorbike     | snowmobile         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, dressmaker, social-worker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, time-travel, crime
1. the social-worker is not to the right of the dressmaker##8
2. the social-worker is on the right of the project-manager##1
3. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the project-manager##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | project-manager | social-worker | dressmaker |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action | time-travel    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, musical, disaster
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, lizard
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
4. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | disaster | western |
| Pet           | goat    | lizard      | goldfish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, mechanic, entrepreneur
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5
3. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
4. the mechanic is on the left of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | mechanic | freelancer | entrepreneur |
| Pet   | goldfish        | cat   | rabbit     |

