.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, software-developer, journalist
1. the software-developer is between the journalist and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the journalist##8
3. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the journalist##8
4. the journalist is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate | lemonade |
| Job        | journalist      | software-developer    | freelancer |

