3. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
4. the pakistani is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | canadian    | pakistani |
