.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: onion, garlic, strawberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, epic, musical
1. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching epic movies is not to the right of the person eating onion##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | strawberry | onion  | garlic |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | epic | musical   |

