2. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | fanta        | iced-tea    |
| Sport      | rugby  | parkour | handball |

