The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, board-games, video-games
1. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
3. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | coffee     | fanta | hot-chocolate   |
| Hobby      | video-games | board-games | rock-climbing |

