.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, metal, punk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, golf, swimming
1. the fan of punk is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of punk is between the fan of metal and the fan of soul##2
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the fan of metal is not to the left of the person who's sport is golf##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | punk      | metal |
| Sport         | cricket | golf | swimming     |

