.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-18::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, carrot, mango
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, goldfish
1. the owner of the pony is not the person eating lettuce##6
2. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | carrot | mango | lettuce    |
| Pet    | pony   | bird      | goldfish |

