.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, martial-arts, time-travel
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, japanese
1. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
2. the japanese is the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the chinese##8
5. the chinese is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | time-travel    | martial-arts  |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese | chinese |

