.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, photography, singing
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, russian, argentine
1. the russian is somewhere between the argentine and the person who's hobby is singing##7
2. the japanese is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
3. the japanese is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | fishing | photography | singing |
| Nationality   | argentine  | russian    | japanese    |

 